   "body" : "First 2 commits avoid unlock/lock `mempool.cs` and `cs_main` interchangeably by turning a loop in two loops - each mutex is locked throughout each corresponding loop.\r\n\r\nThen explicit lock in `CTxMemPool::RemoveUnbroadcastTx`, `CTxMemPool::GetUnbroadcastTxs` and `CTxMemPool::exists` is removed forcing just 3 explicit `WITH_LOCK` where `exists()` is called and just 1 where `GetUnbroadcastTxs()` is called. This can be improved by adding an auxiliary function that locks and calls the original.",
